::GoldenEye/KitKat:;

GoldenEye"
She flew down and landed near KitKat,  She transformed and looked at 
Kitkat. "Your hurt, let's get you to the ship Commander."
She took KitKat by the arm wasn tried to lead her to the ship.


KitKat:
She puched GoldenEye away. "I don't need help.  I need my troops to 
get to teh ship. THAT'S AN ORDER!"

GoldenEye:
She looked at KitKat with a strange look on her face. She sighed and 
responed,"Yes Commander."  She ran over to Dollen. "The Commander 
says to retreat. How are you doing love?" She smiled at Dollen and 
fired her optics lazars at the Maximals

KitKat::

She groaned and limped closer to the ship.  She opened her link,
"Paralysis, we are moving towards Phobia's ship.  Please join us 
there.  The alliance may be there to. Don't attack the Alliance, they 
are assisting us as well."

She called out,"STARSCREAM! GET OVER HERE. I NEED YOU TO HELP GET THE 
OTHERS TO THE SHIP! THE BASE IS ABOUT TO EXPLODE!"
She opened her wrist conpartment and pulled out the small black 
remote for the self destruct sequence in the cave.  She smiled,"If we 
can't have our base, no one will."  SHe set the timer for three 
mnutes and then threw the remote down and shot it with her optic 
lazars.  "Now it can't be stopped."  She opened her commlink to the 
Predacons and the Allience.  "The pred cave will explode in three 
minutes.  Get away from the cave now!"

She limped closer to the ship.
